Knowledge Lake orchestrates a number of third-party open-source projects, each
distributed under its own license. These are declared as dependencies in
pyproject.toml and are not redistributed as part of this source tree. Notable
components include (non-exhaustive):

  - Dagster (Apache-2.0)
  - Docling (MIT)
  - Crawl4AI (Apache-2.0)
  - Qdrant client (Apache-2.0)
  - LiteLLM (MIT)
  - DataTrove (Apache-2.0)
  - Polars, DuckDB, PyArrow (MIT / Apache-2.0)

Refer to each dependency's distribution for its authoritative license terms.
